OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,FThe boss of Ryanair has told said that
OL,7,Fas many as one in ten of its flights
OL,8,Fcould be cancelled if the war in Iran
OL,9,Fcontinues, as ITV News Economics
OL,10,FEditor Joel Hills reports
OL,12,FThe chief executive of Ryanair says
OL,13,Fthe airline will not be able to run
OL,14,Fits full summer schedule because of
OL,15,Fjet fuel shortages if the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz remains closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
