OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Michael O'Leary said that if
OL,8,Fthe war in Iran doesn't end "by the
OL,9,Fend of April", he expects European
OL,10,Fairlines to start cutting scheduled
OL,11,Fflights.
OL,13,F"The Strait of Hormuz has been closed
OL,14,Ffor 30 days. If it remains closed for
OL,15,F60 or 90 days, then we're all facing
OL,16,Fan unknown scenario, and we are
OL,17,Fcertainly looking at maybe having to
OL,18,Fcancel 5%`10% of flights through May,
OL,19,FJune and July," he said.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@MO]uD@AOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
