OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,FO'Leary explained that airlines won't
OL,7,Fbe able to choose which routes to
OL,8,Fcancel - cuts will depend on which
OL,9,Fairports suffer fuel shortages.
OL,11,FHe said he expects to have only a few
OL,12,Fdays' notice from jet fuel suppliers,
OL,13,Fmaking disruption hard to manage.
OL,15,FDespite that, he urged passengers to
OL,16,Fbook summer holidays "as quickly as
OL,17,Fthey can".
OL,19,FRyanair CEO Michael O'Leary speaks to
OL,20,FITV News' Joel Hills
OL,26,@xD@VOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
