OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,FHe insisted that most flights will
OL,7,Foperate and warned that delaying
OL,8,Fbooking is more likely to mean paying
OL,9,Fhigher prices as airfares rise.
OL,11,FAccording to data analytics firm
OL,12,FKpler, 18.8 million tonnes of jet fuel
OL,13,Fwere shipped out of the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz last year - a little over a
OL,15,Ffifth of total global seaborne exports.
OL,17,FThe war in Iran means that supply has
OL,18,Fbeen cut off, and the market has since
OL,19,Ftightened further.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
