PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,FChina - the world's second-largest jet
OL,7,Ffuel producer - is restricting
OL,8,Fexports. South Korea, another key
OL,9,Fproducer, has cut output as it
OL,10,Fstruggles to source crude oil to
OL,11,Frefine.
OL,13,FMore tankers are now bringing jet fuel
OL,14,Ffrom the US to Europe, but not on
OL,15,Fanything like the scale necessary to
OL,16,Foffset lost supply.
OL,18,F"Even if the war ends immediately,
OL,19,Fthere's a crunch looming," said
OL,20,FMichelle Bockmann, a maritime analyst
OL,21,Fwith Windward.
OL,26,@zD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
