OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,F"Important refineries in the Gulf, in
OL,7,FKuwait in particular, have been
OL,8,Fdamaged, and it's not clear how long
OL,9,Fit will take to get shipments of jet
OL,10,Ffuel up and running again. Airports in
OL,11,FEurope are really exposed."
OL,13,FIf flights are cut due to fuel
OL,14,Fshortages, O'Leary said Ryanair would
OL,15,Fget passengers to their destination,
OL,16,Feven if it takes a few days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
