CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775181806
OL,3,CRyanair boss warns airline may cut one
OL,4,Cin 10 flights unless war ends soon
OL,6,F"You won't get compensation because
OL,7,Fit's clearly beyond the airline's
OL,8,Fcontrol," he explained. "But we will
OL,9,Fre-accommodate you, get you back, get
OL,10,Fyou out - whatever it's going to be."
OL,12,FAnd if anyone is unlucky enough to
OL,13,Fhave their flight cancelled, O'Leary
OL,14,Fsaid they should blame Trump rather
OL,15,Fthan airlines.
OL,17,F"This has been a poorly judged attack
OL,18,Fon Iran. There doesn't seem to be any
OL,19,Fexit plan at all," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]pD@YOUrD@eO]yD@AOU{D@RO]
